<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 0.9em;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="header">
  <h1>Congratulations! Your Pharmacy Has Been Approved</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
  <p>Dear {{UserName}},</p>

  <p>We are pleased to inform you that your pharmacy registration has been approved by our administrative team. Your account has been successfully verified and your role has been updated to "pharmacy" status.</p>

  <p>You now have access to all pharmacy-specific features and functionalities in our system. You can start managing your inventory, processing prescriptions, and serving your customers through our platform.</p>

  <h3>What's Next?</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Log in to your account using your existing credentials</li>
    <li>Update your pharmacy profile and operating hours</li>
    <li>Set up your inventory</li>
  </ul>

  <a href="{{loginUrl}}" target="_blank" class="button">Click here to sign in</a>

  <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>

  <p>Best regards,<br>
    The NéoSanté Team</p>
</div>

<div class="footer">
  <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
  <p>© 2025 NéoSanté. All rights reserved.</p>
</div>
